{"tid":1578002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人未必去過跑馬地馬場 入黎睇睇","createTime":"2019-09-18T03:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T03:34:21.000Z","uid":33775,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4037bdc488b544947b259093cd1cb6f0c90dd9fe","tid":1578002,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"小弟就住銅鑼灣果頭嘅 成日坐車都經過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見有好多何6C fans想支持佢隻馬<br />\n但又成班人反對話咩困獸鬥<br />\n但其實 冇人叫你地入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗會講到明有300人聚集就會cancel場馬  點解呢<br />\n其實馬場星期三開比公眾入口就得2個架姐<br />\n第一個<br />\n你有會員就係呢度入 圈住果2度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9MT0BGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9MT0BGy.jpg&h=2e2be77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一個就正門黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdhXDUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdhXDUW.jpg&h=93f2ae10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實張圖個AREA係咁大就咁大 <br />\n老實講 唔洗300人 你有100 200人都隨時可以塞爆呢2度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講 你唔需要入去比藍絲圍<br />\n只要好似塞機場咁唔小心太多人搞到郁唔到就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於無啦啦唔想睇馬點返屋企好呢 <br />\n你跟住呢個方向轉左再行多15分鐘左右又出返CWB時代果邊 咩車都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQ0VqBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQ0VqBr.png&h=216d7529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於搞馬場有冇呀 係咪鬼呀 失唔失焦呀 我就討論啦 隔離post大把<br />\n利申 何律師FANS 好想睇佢隻馬跑第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f70be93436bae6f3564f5990242923c0b6ecd2c","tid":1578002,"uid":82993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"呢筆債，佢哋一定要還。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576589</a>"},{"pid":"791b7c763e73843e9d763dee34e2e3729a969836","tid":1578002,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:25:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">提多一句<br />\n唔夠一公里外有跑馬地狗屋<br />\n間狗屋算大 都有十幾廿架車嘅容量<br />\n完全唔建議你地帶裝<br />\n扮住客就算</span>"},{"pid":"777b00c39d3f510097f1daf53325750d00f2181d","tid":1578002,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ebe5f0894dd0fd0bc22084cb021b5fd7a27fd5","tid":1578002,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fa4179d9ea23b576826c7445c9a3e82a754ad1","tid":1578002,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e7f12d7b46e898e594870f19c8f3bfef60aa8d","tid":1578002,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"未入到去其實沿途都有黑警睇場"},{"pid":"3ee82732983f826f6f4220483ba9ab59a23d9062","tid":1578002,"uid":51790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:30:31.000Z","msg":"塞嚟做乜撚呀<br />\n啲馬一早運哂去啦<br />\n你唔俾人入 入面繼續跑<br />\n俾人屌到屎忽開花咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c2880e262811f2ecb2c6b6fec5fe84aef4b050","tid":1578002,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"其實點解又要搞到平民，清楚返自己目標OK？"},{"pid":"68f883893d05dff8712445b0cf4888875db8e4d6","tid":1578002,"uid":256540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:31:10.000Z","msg":"唔好民鬥民，搞到班爛賭鬼發窮惡，真係唔抵玩，大家要珍惜手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，做翻五大訴求好唔好，唔好走翻法國黃背心條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa639206e054e8f68f1d80f12b72a0137710c54","tid":1578002,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl